  m_text: '

    <line-height=140%><size=90%>

    <indent=5%>The ''White Night''
    is a natural phenomenon which occurs in the northernmost parts of Europe. In
    mid-summer, the sun does not set and the sky remains bright at midnight. This
    is often called the ''Midnight Sun''.</indent>

'
